 <abstract><para>This dataset contains GPS locations of flowering trees and shrubs in the Kruger National Park observed during November and December in 2009, 2010, and 2011.  There is also a table showing the observed interactions between plant species and their insect pollinators, with relative magnitude of pollen loads.</para>
</abstract>
